-- TNT Employees Fear Closing of Liege Freight Hub, Dagblad Says
-- B y   M a a i k e   N o o r d h u i s
-- 2012-03-17T12:10:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-17/tnt-employees-fear-closing-of-liege-freight-hub-dagblad-says.html
TNT Express NV (TNTE)  employees fear
closing of the European freight hub in Liege,  Belgium , if  United
Parcel Service Inc. (UPS)  buys the company, Het Financieele Dagblad
reported.  The Dutch and Belgian labor unions demanded job guarantees
for the 2,200 employees at the hub in a letter to Chief
Executive Officer Marie-Christine Lombard and Chairman Antony Burgmans, the newspaper said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maaike Noordhuis in Amsterdam at 
 mnoordhuis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
